[The number of human cases recorded during the year 2000 West Nile virus
outbreak in the USA is now 20 with 2 deaths. However, one of the 20 cases
is a woman resident in Connecticut who experienced headache only and does
not meet the full clinical case definition established by the Centers for
Disease Control and Prevention. - Mod.CP
